      <title>The authenticity of host github com cant be established</title>
      <link href="/post/the-authenticity-of-host-github-com-cant-be-established/"/>
      <url>/post/the-authenticity-of-host-github-com-cant-be-established/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Almış olduğum hatanın giderilmesi için izlenmesi gereken adım aşağıda yer almaktadır.</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ ssh-keyscan github.com &gt;&gt; ~/.ssh/known_hosts</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="gallery">    <div class="fj-gallery  data" data-rowHeight="220" data-limit="10">    <span class="gallery-data">[{"url":"/post/the-authenticity-of-host-github-com-cant-be-established/1.png","alt":"","title":"Resim 1"}]</span>    </div>    <button class="gallery-load-more"><span>Daha Fazla Yükle</span><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-down"></i></button>    </div><p>Kaynaklar</p><ul><li><a href="https://gist.github.com/vikpe/34454d69fe03a9617f2b009cc3ba200b">https://gist.github.com/vikpe</a></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
